#: src/pages/Status.tsx
msgid "Average effective rate over the selected chart range - what Braiins actually charged per PH/day delivered. Computed as the delta-weighted harmonic mean of the bid: SUM(Δconsumed_sat) ÷ SUM(Δconsumed_sat ÷ bid). Under pay-your-bid the bid IS the price, so when the bid is constant across the window this equals the bid exactly; when the bid varies (mid-window edits) it's the spend-weighted average. Periods of zero delivery contribute zero to both sides and don't skew the result. For the current bid price see the NEXT ACTION panel."
msgstr ""

